								<collation>
									<p>Quires of originally 10 leaves each, marked in the left-hand upper corner with Arabic words. Modern restoration, many leaves now stuck on paper.</p>
								</collation>
								<condition>Lacunae after folios: 12, 21, 31, 45, 48, 61, 115.<p>Imperfect at the beginning and at the end. Many lacunae.</p>
									<p>Last portion is considerably damaged.</p>
									<p>Many folios are severely worm-eaten.</p>
